{"tid":1618749,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"禁蒙面法係要用黎嚇怕和理飛","createTime":"2019-10-04T06:27:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T06:41:36.000Z","uid":80972,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c53845745bb604b14dbb934649a525ef789c2f52","tid":1618749,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:27:15.000Z","msg":"前線出得黎就預左有被捕風險，俾人告暴年要坐十年，都唔驚你個一年半年。<br />\n<br />\n禁蒙面法真正嘅用途係等<span style=\"color: red;\">和理飛唔敢參加非法遊行同集會</span>，因為唔蒙面d人會驚被事後算帳。而家政府最解決唔到，點樣令和理飛同前線割席，而家條屎橋就係出禁蒙面法<br />\n<br />\n上有政策，下有對策，好多野可以保護到自己<br />\n1) 蒙面唔得咪喬裝囉，<span style=\"color: red;\">全世界用一樣嘅喬裝，Cap帽+戴黑超+畫鬍鬚(男女都可以畫)</span>，俾Camera/CCTV影到，冇左髮型同眼，同戴口罩一樣咁難認。仲要個個都係同一個造型，好難事後算帳。<br />\n<br />\n2) 一人一傘，擋Cam擋樣。已經喬裝左，有埋遮去擋cam，好難會被人影到相。<br />\n<br />\n我地和理飛係唔會驚你!"},{"pid":"ed66cde6cda3a24e39b9dd2953505b2e3bebe8b0","tid":1618749,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:28:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3fc3310a589f74fad6bed8c9299e55d26bfc65d5","tid":1618749,"uid":25468,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:32:18.000Z","msg":"和理非太陽帽<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/10/04/kMKyle.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F10%2F04%2FkMKyle.png&h=fcdde484&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f49c9f4ac90d7129d7d79e3be2e2731cbd3787d5","tid":1618749,"uid":92353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:37:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25208fdbccb0e81095a86154eae64830de6a40c2","tid":1618749,"uid":269052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:38:01.000Z","msg":"好多和理非都唔戴罩，嚇撚？"},{"pid":"a60515ba3db22d1e73d96d7a61ad7537738af5c4","tid":1618749,"uid":80972,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:41:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Duz9qPB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=